%wrapper
  =render "shared/header"
  .main
    .main__contents
      .main__contents__visual
        .main__contents__visual__title
          人生を変えるフリマアプリ
        .main__contents__visual__subtitle
          FURIMAはだれでもかんたんに出品・購入できる
          %br フリマアプリです
        .main__contents__visual__btn
        =link_to "https://www.apple.com/jp/ios/app-store/" do
          = image_tag "app-store-badge.png",class: "main__contents__visual__btn--apple"
        =link_to "https://play.google.com/store?hl=ja" do
          = image_tag "google-play-badge.png",class:  "main__contents__visual__btn--google"
    .main__reason
      .main__reason__introduction
        .main__reason__introduction__subtitle
          FURIMAが選ばれる３つの理由
        %ul.main__reason__introduction__detail
          %li.main__reason__introduction__detail__cube
          .main__reason__introduction__detail__cube__pic
            %span.number 1
            =image_tag  "pict-reason-01.jpg",class: "main__reason__introduction__detail__cube__pic__bottom"
            .main__reason__introduction__detail__cube__pic__text
              %span 3分
              ですぐに出品
            .main__reason__introduction__detail__cube__pic__description
              スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる!
          .main__reason__introduction__detail__cube__pic
            %span.number 2
            =image_tag  "pict-reason-02.jpg",class: "main__reason__introduction__detail__cube__pic__bottom"
            .main__reason__introduction__detail__cube__pic__text
              %span シンプル
              で使いやすい
            .main__reason__introduction__detail__cube__pic__description
              めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ！
          .main__reason__introduction__detail__cube__pic
            %span.number ３
            =image_tag  "pict-reason-03.jpg",class: "main__reason__introduction__detail__cube__pic__bottom"
            .main__reason__introduction__detail__cube__pic__text
              手数料
              %span 業界最安
            .main__reason__introduction__detail__cube__pic__description
              最大3%でお得に出品&購入！
    .main__middlepic
      .main__middlepic__comment
        .main__middlepic__comment__title
          会員数日本一位
        .main__middlepic__comment__text
          FURIMAは、フリマアプリで最も人気。
          %br 出品・購入回数も業界最多です！
          ほしかったあの商品に出会えるかもしれません。
        .main__middlepic__comment__btn
        =link_to "https://www.apple.com/jp/ios/app-store/" do
          = image_tag "app-store-badge.png",class: "main__contents__visual__btn--apple"
        =link_to "https://play.google.com/store?hl=ja" do
          = image_tag "google-play-badge.png",class:  "main__contents__visual__btn--google"
    .main__future
      .main__future__title
        FURIMAの特徴
      .main__future__items
        .main__future__items__item
          .main__future__items__item__img
            =image_tag  "icon-01.png",  class:  "main__future__items__item__img__detail"
            .main__future__items__item__img__subtitle
              簡単に売り買いできる
            .main__future__items__item__img__text
              スマホひとつで、いつでもどこでも簡単に出品・購入が可能！
          .main__future__items__item__img
            =image_tag  "icon-02.png",  class:  "main__future__items__item__img__detail"
            .main__future__items__item__img__subtitle
              売上金は即日振込みに対応
            .main__future__items__item__img__text
              午前9時までに振込を依頼いただければ、翌日に指定の口座に入金いたします!
          .main__future__items__item__img
            =image_tag  "icon-03.png",  class:  "main__future__items__item__img__detail"
            .main__future__items__item__img__subtitle
              様々な支払いに対応
            .main__future__items__item__img__text
              お支払いは、クレジットカードだけでなく、ポイントや売上金など多彩な方法があります。
    .main__pickup
      .main__pickup__head
        ピックアップカテゴリー
      .main__pickup__product
        .main__pickup__product__head
          = link_to "#",class:"list"  do
            %h3 新規投稿商品
        .main__pickup__product__lists
          - @items.each do |item|
            .main__pickup__product__lists
              .main__pickup__product__lists__list
                = link_to item_path(item.id) do
                  = image_tag "#{item.item_images[0].src}" ,class: "main__pickup__product__lists__list__img"
                    -if item.buyer.present?
                    売り切れました
                .main__pickup__product__lists__list__text
                  .main__pickup__product__lists__list__text__name
                  = item.name
                  .main__pickup__product__lists__list__text__detail
                  %ul
                    %li= ('¥' + item.price.to_s(:delimited))
                    %li.fav
                      %i.fas.fa-star 
                      1
                  %p (税込)
      .main__pickup__head
        ピックアップブランド
      .main__pickup__product
        .main__pickup__product__head
          = link_to "#",class:"list" do
            %h3 アーカイバ
        .main__pickup__product__lists
          - @items.each do |item|
            .main__pickup__product__lists
              .main__pickup__product__lists__list
                = link_to item_path(item.id) do
                  = image_tag "#{item.item_images[0].src}" ,class: "main__pickup__product__lists__list__img"
                    -if item.buyer.present? 
                    売り切れました
                .main__pickup__product__lists__list__text
                  .main__pickup__product__lists__list__text__name
                  = item.name
                  .main__pickup__product__lists__list__text__detail
                  %ul
                    %li= ('¥' + item.price.to_s(:delimited))
                    %li.fav
                      %i.fas.fa-star 
                      1
                  %p (税込)



  =render  "shared/footer"